sen paul simon dill agreed up to a point 
we do not yet know the full relationship between lowlevel 
radiation and latent illness he said but it is crystal clear 
that many of those responsible for setting policies that affect 
thousands of our citizens are intent upon making the facts fit 
their theories and decisions instead of the other way around 
