been on an even more intensive scale than before 
un experts examined victims in iran and iraq and concluded 
most were suffering from exposure to mustard gas a world war iera 
agent a few had been exposed to a nerve gas the experts said 
the team said they examined 39 iraqi victims all military 
personnel and 66 iranians both soldiers and civilians 
iran claims iraqi victims were exposed to poisonous gases used 
