the team set out from the northernmost tip of siberia on march 3 
and hopes to complete the 1100mile trek through some of the 
worlds most hostile terrain by reaching cape columbia on canadas 
ellesmere island in early june they arrived at the geographic 
north pole at 320 am edt tuesday the 55th day of their 
adventure 
